{"tid":505992,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"睇黎韓狗已經反智到常人難以理解既地步","createTime":"2017-12-21T17:15:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T15:36:15.000Z","uid":74858,"like":68,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"996984a05c71d509235daf0d0f5b44c7d4b50856","tid":505992,"uid":74858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T17:15:52.000Z","msg":"韓國歌手鐘鉉出殯，不少歌迷聲稱拍攝到與 SHINee 應援色一樣的「湖水綠月亮」<br />\n<br />\n韓國男子組合 SHINee 的成員鐘鉉於本週一自殺身亡，今日出殯，並由隊友扶靈。各界都深感惋惜，而在日本，不少鐘鉉的歌迷聲稱拍攝到天上出現「湖水綠月亮」。在日韓文化中，流行以指定顏色代表藝人或組合，而湖水綠色正是 SHINee 的「應援色」，因此有不少歌迷認為，「湖水綠月亮」是鐘鉉留下的最後禮物，並貼出照片表達對鐘鉉的思念與不捨。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/shinee_ayasannsann3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2Fshinee_ayasannsann3.jpg&h=8f661423&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有少少常識都知拎住部機對光影有炫光啦<br />\n清朝都冇咁迷信<br />\n講出黎唔撚覺得肉麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://photoblog.hk/194857/%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E6%89%8B%E9%90%98%E9%89%89%E5%87%BA%E6%AE%AF%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%91%E6%AD%8C%E8%BF%B7%E8%81%B2%E7%A8%B1%E6%8B%8D%E6%94%9D%E5%88%B0%E8%88%87-shinee-%E6%87%89%E6%8F%B4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2F194857%2F%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25AD%258C%25E6%2589%258B%25E9%2590%2598%25E9%2589%2589%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%25AE%25AF%25EF%25BC%258C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B0%2591%25E6%25AD%258C%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E8%2581%25B2%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%258B%258D%25E6%2594%259D%25E5%2588%25B0%25E8%2588%2587-shinee-%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%258F%25B4%2F&d=nL7egrjVVTLOIcUIcKoS8Nr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=3d91e280\" target=\"_blank\">https://photoblog.hk/194857/%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E6%89%8B%E9%90%98%E9%89%89%E5%87%BA%E6%AE%AF%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5